<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Formal Monographs (LaTeX)</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><em>Process, Projection, and Power</em> — unified ontology via KES framework, synthesizing Forrest Landry's process metaphysics with RSVP and Spherepop</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><em>Identity After Collapse</em> — formal theory of self-reference and fixed points in Spherepop</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><em>Possibility and History / Identity as Event History</em> — 82-page merged ontology of irreversible processes</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Games &amp; Interactive Tools</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Plenum Crown</strong> — civilization-strategy game prototype grounded in RSVP field dynamics</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Blastoids Pic Breeder</strong> — browser-based evolutionary image selection using CLIP embeddings</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Blastoids Tunnel Shooter</strong> — 3D tunnel shooter game using the 5,000-image Stable Diffusion corpus</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Platforms &amp; Infrastructure</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Zebra/ZebraTube</strong> — text analysis and collaborative media platform (Python CLI + React/FastAPI)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>RSVP Writing Toolkit</strong> — compositional writing tools tied to the RSVP framework</li>
</ul>
