ger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.tex</code> source is written — ~1,300 lines covering all 9 sections plus two appendices, with theorem environments, TikZ figures, and the full formal apparatus. One minor package conflict remains to resolve before it compiles clean: there's an option clash with <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">parskip</code> (caused by loading it twice via two different methods). Here's the fix needed in the preamble:</p>
